The,Oil,Price,Information,Service,OPIS,is,the,world,s,most,comprehensive,source,for,petroleum,pricing,and,news,information,They,maintain,a,database,of,U,S,wholesale,petroleum,prices,receiving,more,than,rack,prices,each,day,The,OPIS,API,lets,users,connect,to,a,web,service,to,query,the,site,database,The,Database,is,updated,in,real,time,and,the,data,can,be,integrated,into,a,user,s,web,site,Documentation,is,not,publicly,available